  • Constructor Details

    • Phase

      public Phase​(GameEngine p_gameEngine)
      Represents a phase in the game. All game phases extend this class and implement specific behaviors for each phase. This abstract class defines the methods common to all game phases.
      Parameters:
      p_gameEngine - The GameEngine instance that manages the game.
